  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study was to evaluate the potential of L-PRF in increasing the width of the
      keratinsed mucosa around implants. Furthermore, it was assessed whether this surgery was
      associated with significantly less post-operative discomfort for the patient compared to Free
      Gingival Graft surgery. L-PRF for increasing keratinised mucosa around implants.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
